OL,5, The boss of retailer Next is urging the
OL,6, government to let more foreign workers 
OL,7, into the UK to ease labour shortages.  
OL,9,FLord Wolfson, who was a prominent      
OL,10,Fadvocate of Brexit, said the UK's      
OL,11,Fcurrent immigration policy was         
OL,12,Fcrippling economic growth.             
OL,14,FHe said firms should pay a tax to      
OL,15,Femploy foreign workers, to encourage   
OL,16,Fthem to recruit from the UK first.     
OL,18,FThe government said it had delivered on
OL,19,Fits promise to "take back control of   
OL,20,Four immigration system".               
